lyric:
[00:00.000] 作词 : Ella Marie Hætta Isaksen/Gunnar Greve/Øyvind Sauvik
[00:01.000] 作曲 : Alan Walker/James Njie/Sander Meland/Fredrik Borch Olsen/Marcus Arnbekk/Ella Marie Hætta Isaksen/Gunnar Greve/Øyvind Sauvik
[00:10.867]Confetti is falling at 5 in the morning
[00:16.425]They’re screaming and crying
[00:19.085]But I’m all by myself
[00:21.866]I know you, I’m sorry
[00:24.572]I made up a story
[00:27.137]I’m lonely, I’m falling
[00:29.950]Just like you, I’m sorry

tlyric:
[by:正参]
[00:10.867]五彩碎屑 飘零落下 清晨五点
[00:16.425]他们尖叫 哭号着
[00:19.085]而我却 独自一人
[00:21.866]很抱歉 我了解你的情况
[00:24.572]于是我编造了个故事
[00:27.137]我十分孤独 我正在坠落
[00:29.950]就像你一样 我很抱歉
